summary: Experienced Teacher with a demonstrated history of working in secondary education. Also working in vocational education for one day a week. Mixing past experiences with the challenges and chances of present and future. ''Bildung'' in every kind of way! Skilled in Curriculum Development, Creative Teaching, Educational Leadership, Teacher Training, German, and English. Strong educational professional with a Master of Education - MEd  in German Language and Literature from NHL Hogeschool.
